abstract: Phillip Alder Bridge column on deal played by the winners of the Machlin Women's Swiss Teams in Memphis.
lead_paragraph: The winners of the Machlin Women’s Swiss Teams in Memphis last month were Barbara Sonsini of Woodside, Calif.; Judi Radin of New York City; Lynn Deas of Schenectady, N.Y.; Beth Palmer of Chevy Chase, Md.; Irina Levitina of Hackensack, N.J.; and Kerri Sanborn of Stony Point, N.Y.
